<main class="container review-detail-page"><div class="breadcrumb nav-title"><span class="active">任务四：定位和居中问题（<a href="/task/detail?taskId=4">查看详情</a>）</span></div><div class="main"><div class="submit-group-info"><h4>团队：<a href="/group/profile?groupId=983" target="_blank">三文鱼</a></h4><p class="submit-basic"><span class="submit-time"><a href="/user/profile?userId=2199">吴灿丽</a>&nbsp;更新于<em>03-20 18:00</em></span><span class="review-num">已经有<em>7</em>人 review</span><span class="score">平均得分：<em>9.29</em></span></p><p>代码地址：<a href="https://github.com/cherry037/task4" target="_blank">https://github.com/cherry037/task4</a></p><p>demo：<a href="http://cherry037.github.io/task4" target="_blank">http://cherry037.github.io/task4</a></p><p class="submit-descr">我们这种居中方法是用在元素不定宽高的情况下，随着浏览器窗口的变化，宽高也随之改变。请大家多多点评讨论。</p></div><ul class="review-result-list container-fluid"><li class="row review-result" data-id="1448"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=4100" target="_blank">前进进前</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-28 18:17</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=10642" target="_blank">何蟠</a>&nbsp;03-28 18:17&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">8</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">外面的灰色盒子如果按照你里面的那个绝对定位方法就可以搞定极端情况了吧，按百分比来定位而不是具体的像素。</span></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="1440"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=3658" target="_blank">泮池码农</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-28 17:05</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=9643" target="_blank">魏银平</a>&nbsp;03-28 17:05&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">10</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">学习了</span></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="1348"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=210" target="_blank">望楼</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-26 22:31</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=823" target="_blank">徐淑云</a>&nbsp;03-26 22:31&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">8</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">很想知道在固定元素的宽高下是怎么居中，有谁有更好的办法不</span><ul class="reply-wrap"><li class="reply"style="display:block;" data-id=578><p class="reply-info"><a href="/user/profile?userId=4554">周佳敏</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-28 19:34</span></p><p class="reply-content">我们组采用了下面这种方式：<br />
.backg{<br />
   width: 400px;<br />
   height: 200px;<br />
   background: #ccc;<br />
   position:fixed;<br />
   margin:auto;<br />
   left:0;<br />
   right:0;<br />
   top:0;<br />
   bottom:0;<br />
   overflow:hidden;<br />
}  <br />
但不知道更优的还有什么？<br />
如果知道了希望回复一下！谢谢！</p></li><li class="reply" data-id=553><p class="reply-info">作者<a href="/user/profile?userId=2671">陈晛</a>&nbsp;回复&nbsp;<span class="time">03-27 16:05</span></p><p class="reply-content">首先感谢评价，我们团队的方法其实更灵活一些，对元素的宽高没有限制，这相对更难一些。至于固定宽高的，方法有很多，提供一种思路，可以在目标定位的盒子外面再套一个父盒子。父盒子的宽高与子盒子一致。然后先对父盒子设置绝对定位，left和top各百分之五十，然后子盒子也设置绝对定位，left和top各负百分之五十从而最终实现子盒子水平垂直居中效果。</p></li><li class="show-more"><button class="more-btn btn btn-link">显示全部（共<em>2</em>条评论）</button></li></ul></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="1259"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=638" target="_blank">宇宙工业大学</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-25 18:02</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=1521" target="_blank">钱秋何</a>&nbsp;03-25 18:02&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">9</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">没有考虑极端情况</span></div></li><li class="row review-result" data-id="1209"><div class="review-user clearfix"><span class="pull-left"><a href="/group/profile?groupId=691" target="_blank">XD微客</a><span class="time-info">review&nbsp;<span class="time">03-24 23:12</span><span class="update-time">（<a href="/user/profile?userId=1692" target="_blank">王璇</a>&nbsp;03-24 23:12&nbsp;更新）</span></span></span><span class="pull-right score-info"><span class="score text-success">10</span><span class="text-muted">分</span></span></div><div class="review-comment"><span class="comment">box水平垂直居中的方法用的好棒！<br />
